shortdesc Supplementary outer and inner themes for beamer
longdesc This bundle provides a collection of inner and outer themes as
longdesc supplements to the default themes in the beamer distribution.
longdesc These themes can be used in combination with existing inner,
longdesc outer, and color themes.
